response.overview: Morning Musume Concert Tour 2013 Haru Michishige☆Eleven SOUL ~Tanaka Reina Sotsugyou Kinenbi~ in Nippon Budokan is a DVD and Blu-ray released by Morning Musume. It features footage from their spring 2013 concert tour on May 28, 2013 at Nippon Budokan, including the graduation of Tanaka Reina.
